com.revature.jfbennatt.ers.controller.delegates

Class ViewDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.jfbennatt.ers.controller.delegates.Delegate
      • com.revature.jfbennatt.ers.controller.delegates.ViewDelegate

  • public class ViewDelegate
extends Delegate
    This routes requests for pages (e.g. /) to the appropriate static page. This needs to communicate with the RequestDispatcher so should be explicitly declared (i.e. not as a Delegate).
    Author:
    Jared F Bennatt
